<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
<title>Homework Tracker - St. Joseph’s Asharadhama ICSE School</title>
<style>
  body {
    font-family: 'Georgia', serif;
    background: #fdf6e3;
    color: #333;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    min-height: 100vh;
  }
  .container {
    width: 90%;
    max-width: 800px;
    background: #fff;
    padding: 30px 40px;
    margin: 40px 0;
    border-radius: 12px;
    box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
  }
  header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 25px;
  }
  header img {
    height: 60px;
    margin-right: 15px;
  }
  header h1 {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    color: #2c3e50;
    margin: 0;
  }
  label {
    display: block;
    margin-top: 15px;
    font-weight: bold;
  }
  input[type="text"], input[type="date"], select, textarea {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 10px;
    margin-top: 6px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border: 1px solid #ccc;
    font-family: 'Georgia', serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    box-sizing: border-box;
  }
  textarea {
    resize: vertical;
    min-height: 80px;
    background: #fff8f0;
  }
  button {
    margin-top: 20px;
    padding: 12px 25px;
    background: #2c3e50;
    color: white;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 10px;
    font-size: 1rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: background-color 0.25s ease;
  }
  button:hover {
    background: #34495e;
  }
  table {
    width: 100%;
    margin-top: 30px;
    border-collapse: collapse;
  }
  th, td {
    padding: 12px 15px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
    text-align: left;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    vertical-align: top;
  }
  th {
    background: #f0e5d8;
    color: #2c3e50;
  }
  /* Export PDF button style */
  #exportPdfBtn {
    background: #2980b9;
    color: #fff;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 12px 25px;
    cursor: pointer;
    margin-top: 10px;
  }
  #exportPdfBtn:hover {
    background: #1f618d;
  }
</style>

<!-- jsPDF library -->
<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/jspdf/2.5.1/jspdf.umd.min.js"></script>

</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <header>
      <img src="logo.png" alt="School Logo" id="schoolLogo" />
      <h1>St. Joseph’s Asharadhama ICSE School</h1>
    </header>

    <form id="homeworkForm">
      <label for="assignedDate">Date Assigned:</label>
      <input type="date" id="assignedDate" name="assignedDate" required />

      <label for="day">Day:</label>
      <input type="text" id="day" name="day" readonly />

      <label for="classGrade">Class/Grade:</label>
      <input type="text" id="classGrade" name="classGrade" placeholder="e.g. 7A" required />

      <label for="subject">Subject:</label>
      <input type="text" id="subject" name="subject" placeholder="e.g. Mathematics" required />

      <label for="description">Description:</label>
      <textarea id="description" name="description" placeholder="Describe the homework/task" required></textarea>

      <button type="submit">Add Homework</button>
    </form>

    <table id="homeworkTable" aria-label="Homework list">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Date Assigned</th>
          <th>Day</th>
          <th>Class/Grade</th>
          <th>Subject</th>
          <th>Description</th>
          <th>Action</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody></tbody>
    </table>

    <button id="exportPdfBtn">Export as PDF</button>
  </div>

<script>
  const form = document.getElementById('homeworkForm');
  const assignedDateInput = document.getElementById('assignedDate');
  const dayInput = document.getElementById('day');
  const tbody = document.querySelector('#homeworkTable tbody');

  function getDayName(dateString) {
    const date = new Date(dateString);
    return date.toLocaleDateString('en-US', { weekday: 'long' });
  }

  function updateDay() {
    if (assignedDateInput.value) {
      dayInput.value = getDayName(assignedDateInput.value);
    } else {
      dayInput.value = '';
    }
  }

  window.onload = () => {
    const today = new Date().toISOString().split('T')[0];
    assignedDateInput.value = today;
    updateDay();
    loadHomework();
  };

  assignedDateInput.addEventListener('change', updateDay);

  function getHomeworkList() {
    return JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem('homeworkList') || '[]');
  }

  function saveHomeworkList(list) {
    localStorage.setItem('homeworkList', JSON.stringify(list));
  }

  function renderHomework() {
    const list = getHomeworkList();
    tbody.innerHTML = '';

    if (list.length === 0) {
      tbody.innerHTML = '<tr><td colspan="6" style="text-align:center; color:#888;">No homework assigned yet.</td></tr>';
      return;
    }

    list.forEach((hw, index) => {
      const tr = document.createElement('tr');

      tr.innerHTML = `
        <td>${hw.assignedDate}</td>
        <td>${hw.day}</td>
        <td>${hw.classGrade}</td>
        <td>${hw.subject}</td>
        <td>${hw.description}</td>
        <td>
          <button onclick="deleteHomework(${index})" style="background:#e74c3c; color:#fff; border:none; border-radius:5px; padding:5px 10px; cursor:pointer;">
            Delete
          </button>
        </td>
      `;

      tbody.appendChild(tr);
    });
  }

  function deleteHomework(index) {
    if (confirm('Are you sure you want to delete this homework?')) {
      const list = getHomeworkList();
      list.splice(index, 1);
      saveHomeworkList(list);
      renderHomework();
    }
  }

  form.addEventListener('submit', e => {
    e.preventDefault();

    const newHomework = {
      assignedDate: form.assignedDate.value,
      day: form.day.value,
      classGrade: form.classGrade.value.trim(),
      subject: form.subject.value.trim(),
      description: form.description.value.trim()
    };

    const list = getHomeworkList();
    list.push(newHomework);
    saveHomeworkList(list);
    form.reset();

    // Reset date & day to today after form submit
    const today = new Date().toISOString().split('T')[0];
    assignedDateInput.value = today;
    updateDay();

    renderHomework();
  });

  function loadHomework() {
    renderHomework();
  }

  // Export PDF button with wrapped description
  
</script>

<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/jspdf/2.5.1/jspdf.umd.min.js"></script>
<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/jspdf-autotable/3.5.28/jspdf.plugin.autotable.min.js"></script>

<script>
  document.getElementById('exportPdfBtn').addEventListener('click', () => {
    const { jsPDF } = window.jspdf;
    const doc = new jsPDF();

    const homeworkList = JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem('homeworkList') || '[]');
    if (homeworkList.length === 0) {
      alert('No homework data to export!');
      return;
    }

    const logoBase64 = "data:image/png;base64,";

    doc.addImage(logoBase64, 'PNG', 10, 10, 30, 30);
    doc.setFontSize(16);
    doc.setTextColor(44, 62, 80);
    doc.text("St. Joseph’s Asharadhama ICSE School", 50, 20);
    doc.setFontSize(12);
    doc.text("Learning Tracker Report", 50, 30);

    const tableHeaders = [['Date Assigned', 'Day', 'Class', 'Subject', 'Description']];
    const tableBody = homeworkList.map(hw => [
      hw.assignedDate,
      hw.day,
      hw.classGrade,
      hw.subject,
      hw.description
    ]);

    doc.autoTable({
      startY: 40,
      head: tableHeaders,
      body: tableBody,
      styles: {
        fontSize: 10,
        textColor: [40, 40, 40],
        lineColor: [200, 200, 200],
        lineWidth: 0.2
      },
      headStyles: {
        fillColor: [240, 229, 216],
        textColor: [44, 62, 80],
        fontStyle: 'bold'
      },
      alternateRowStyles: {
        fillColor: [250, 250, 250]
      },
      theme: 'grid',
      margin: { top: 40 }
    });

    doc.save("Learning_Tracker_Report.pdf");
  });
</script>
</body>
</html>
